Text: FW PerformanceMessage From shawn donlin SMTPsePaineWebbercom Sent Monday December PM To Subject FW Performance Thank you for confirming to me your Email address Here is the nd attempt I am sorry you did not receive this info the first time I will send the physical backup to your home address per our phone conversation today Thanks again Shawn Original Message From shawn donlin SMTPsePaineWebbercom Sent Wednesday November PM To Subject Performance Per your conversation with Pat Dowd please find attached two versions of the performance figures for your accounts We ran the return numbers two ways Sheet was calculated by subracting the ending balance from the beginning balance less deposits and withdrawals then divided by the beginning balance Sheet was calculated by dividing the earnings by the total investment Youll also find the historical performance of the indices that you requested at the end of each sheet Feel free to modify the sheets to fit your needs let us know if you require any further information I will forward you the physical backup statements etc to follow Happy Thanksgiving Notice Regarding Entry of Orders and Instructions Please do not transmit orders andor instructions regarding your PaineWebber accounts by email Orders andor instructions transmitted by email will not be accepted by PaineWebber and PaineWebber will not be responsible for carrying out such orders andor instructions Notice Regarding Privacy and Confidentiality PaineWebber reserves the right to monitor and review the content of all email communications sent andor received by its employees Schwiegerxls
